Parliament, Monday, 15 July 2019 – A joint meeting of the Standing Committee on Public Accounts (Scopa) and the Standing Committee on the Auditor-General (SCOAG) will tomorrow be briefed by the Auditor-General of South Africa on the Municipal Audit Outcomes for the 2016/2017 financial year. Details of the meeting are as follows:
	Date: Tuesday, 16 July 2019
	Time: 09:30
	Venue: Good Hope Chamber, Good Hope Building
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF SCOPA, MR MKHULEKO HLENGWA, AND THE CHAIRPERSON OF SCOAG, MR SAKHUMZI SOMYO.
	
	For media enquiries, please contact the committees’ Media Officer:
	Name: Ms Faith Ndenze
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8062
	Cell: 081 377 0686
